# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ALLOWLIST gitignore for the insights ROUTINE repo.
# This workspace holds customer PII (emails in docs, notebooks, CSVs) and live
# secrets (.env). To push a clean, PII-free repo for the cloud routine we ignore
# EVERYTHING by default and re-include only the safe, self-contained framework.
# `git status` after init must show ONLY insights/ + these support files.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# 1. Ignore everything at the repo root.
/*

# 2. Re-include only the safe set.
!/.gitignore
!/README_ROUTINE.md
!/requirements-insights.txt
!/insights/

# 3. Within insights/, drop caches and local-only artifacts.
insights/__pycache__/
insights/**/__pycache__/

# Never, under any circumstance:
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
